      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable for daily commutes and still looks great in the driveway. The interior is nice and clean, and it drives like a dream! It\u2019s had a lot of love, so there's a tiny bit of character here and there, but nothing that stops it from being a fantastic car for its next owner. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
