    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS rebuild and rod bearing service, ensuring the mechanical integrity of the rotating assembly. The chassis exhibits precise handling characteristics with no subframe fatigue. While the finish shows light road wear consistent with its age, the performance remains uncompromised, offering the visceral feedback and mechanical purity synonymous with the M-division\u2019s golden era.",
