    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2019 Executive Touring Sedan is a prime example of a well-maintained luxury vehicle that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though there are a few minor, unavoidable stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel consistent with respectful use. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the genuine perforated leather upholstery is clean and supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the adaptive cruise control and navigation system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a complete folder of service records showing oil changes every 5,000 miles. The brakes are firm, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been primarily garage-kept, offering the next owner a sophisticated driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
